profile:
At Reliance, the safety and well-being of both our Customers and our Team Members is always our top priority. We are actively monitoring the Coronavirus (COVID-19) situation and are taking precautionary measures to aid in keeping our communities safe. We have implemented strict safety protocols to provide both our Customers and Team members with peace of mind during this challenging time. We continue to provide the exceptional customer experiences we are synonymous for and want you to know that we are here for you when you need us.

Reliance Home Comfort has been delivering high quality home comfort products and services for over 40 years. Specializing in furnaces, air conditioners, water heaters and plumbing, we provide our customers with peace of mind and are with you every step of the way. When you choose Reliance, you’re choosing one of the largest HVAC providers in Canada, with over 1.7 million customers and growing. You can expect your call to be answered 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. With one of the largest networks of licensed technicians in Canada, we respond to over 500,000 service calls each year. 
After all, we believe you are investing in much more than home comfort equipment, you’re investing in a relationship and your satisfaction is our top priority.
888-837-1451 is a TOLL FREE No., please feel free to contact!!

profile:
Whether the purpose is for residential or commercial usage, you want to make sure that your HVAC system is in working order and Smart Comfort Heating & Cooling wants the same.  This isn’t just a matter of staying comfortable; it’s a matter of staying safe!  Getting too hot or cold can cause injury, even if you’re indoors.

If a problem comes up and your HVAC system breaks down, the good news is that you can get quick heating and cooling service.  Rapid response is especially important during times of extreme weather.

Smart Comfort Heating & Cooling is a qualified HVAC contractor in the Thunder Bay, ON area. We are licensed and experienced to get the job done right. Taking the risk of getting someone who doesn’t really know how to fix the machine in question can be costly down the road, and even potentially dangerous. At Smart Comfort Heating & Cooling, we specialize in both AC and heating service for your home or office.

HVAC repair is definitely not a do-it-yourself job. The air conditioner is a complicated piece of machinery that’s best left to the experts. To work properly, it has to be correctly attached to your home’s power source and ventilation system, which is not an easy thing to do.  You’ll save yourself a lot of trouble by hiring a professional.

If you don’t have a working HVAC system, you should get a heating and air conditioning repair right away!  Having a good one in your home can actually increase its resale value.  Once again, getting the job done is a matter of hiring the right people.

We also have professionals that can assist with any air duct cleaning, furnace repair, and boiler service. Our clients in Thunder Bay, ON trust us with a wide array of repairs and services.

If you’re looking to keep your home appliances in good working order, then you can get help from Smart Comfort Heating & Cooling. We can respond quickly and effectively to any HVAC situation.
